💡 Placement Tip

Arithmetic Progression is a favorite topic in aptitude tests because the formulas are straightforward but require careful substitution. Memorize the nth term formula, the sum formula, and the middle-term trick, and practice quick calculations. Most AP questions in placement exams can be solved in under a minute with enough practice.
